&lt;p&gt;Civitas Learning is looking for a highly professional and confident individual to join our Customer Support team.&amp;nbsp;As a &lt;strong&gt;PeopleSoft Engineer,&lt;/strong&gt; you will serve as the primary technical expert bridging the gap between our software and our customers&#39; PeopleSoft ecosystems. Your focus will be on ensuring the &lt;em&gt;seamless&lt;/em&gt; interoperability and data flow between platforms, diagnosing complex connectivity issues within PeopleSoft HCM and Campus Solutions environments to support our software&#39;s success.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do as a PeopleSoft Engineer:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the lead technical point of contact to resolve synchronization and connectivity issues between our software and PeopleSoft.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze customer-specific PeopleSoft components, such as Integration Broker, PeopleCode, and Application Engine, to troubleshoot why data is not transferring correctly to our platform.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we are looking for:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of hands-on PeopleSoft development experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience working with PeopleSoft Campus Solutions modules in addition to HCM or Financials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in Agile environments and utilizing tools like Jira for task management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with Oracle databases and SQL.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with PeopleSoft Fluid UI and integrating PeopleSoft with third-party systems via APIs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technical Skills:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PeopleSoft Development: PeopleCode, Application Designer, SQR, Application Engine, Integration Broker, and Component Interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Functional Knowledge: Familiarity with Campus Solutions (CS), HCM, or FSCM business processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Databases: Oracle databases and SQL script optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PeopleSoft Maintenance: PeopleSoft Update Manager (PUM) and Change Assistant.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll get:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;100% remote work environment with the ability to work from anywhere (availability during U.S. business hours required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Unlimited, flexible PTO&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Every other Friday off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly stipend for home office&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous parental leave policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;*Please note that this position is structured to begin on a &lt;strong&gt;Part-Time basis&lt;/strong&gt;. Our goal is to transition this into a &lt;strong&gt;Full-Time role (40 hours per week)&lt;/strong&gt; upon the successful completion of initial projects. We are looking for a candidate with the immediate capacity and long-term desire to grow into a full-time role.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Part-time hours paid at a pro-rata rate of the full-time base. Upon successful transition, the salary will move to the full-time range of 50.000 - 60.000 per year.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Remote - LATAM&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$50,000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$60,000 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY WE LOVE WHAT WE DO:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Civitas Learning, we seek to help colleges and universities apply their vast student data to maximize institutional impact and improve the student outcomes that matter most.&lt;/p&gt;
